spec_data.Name: dxcc-gui
spec_data.Description:
dxcc-gui is a small utility which determines the ARRL DXCC entity of a amateur
radio callsign, based on the cty.dat country file by Jim Reisert, AD1C.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 04:05:26 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Optional GUI with a world map showing the DXCC's location
